column11:
  In this paper, we investigate the generalized Hyers-Ulam stability of the
following reciprocal type functional equation
\begin{equation*}f(2x+y)+f(2x-y)=\frac{2f(x)f(y)\displaystyle{\sum_{\substack{k=0\\
\text{$k$ is even}}}^{
l}2^{l-k}\binom{l}{k}f(x)^{\frac{k}{l}}f(y)^{\frac{l-k}{l}}}}{\left(4f(y)^{\frac{2}{l}}-f(x)^{\frac{2}{l}}\right)^l}\end{equation*}
in non-zero real and non-Archimedean spaces.
